race.comment: MISS MILA (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 388m behind Kilcoy Castle (22.69) in a Mix 1/2/3. Looks the one to beat on her best form. IVY'S MIGHT (5) doesn't win out of turn. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (18.37) at Richmond. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Expecting another good run. GAMBINO (8) should get a clear run from the wide draw. Safely held last start when a 4.5 lengths 6th at Richmond Straight (17.71). Form here at this distance is strong including eight wins. Can do much better this time. MISS LOUELLA (2) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.
